---
import Bi from '../shared/Bi.astro';
import Callout from '../shared/Callout.astro';
import Section from '../mechanics/Section.astro';
---
<Section id="task-bonuses" titleZh="任務獎勵：新手免費資源" titleEn="Task rewards: free starter resources" eyebrow="Day 0–14">
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="開新帳號會出現任務系統（Adviser quests），每完成一個給資源 / 銀幣 / 物品。Lumi 強調「Spawn village 拿全部 task bonus」是早期最高 ROI 之一，因為相對於建造成本，獎勵超大。"
      en="New accounts get an Adviser quest system; each completed task rewards resources / silver / items. Lumi emphasizes 'grab every task bonus on spawn village' as one of the highest-ROI activities early game — rewards are huge relative to the actions required."
    />
  </p>

  <h3><Bi zh="任務類型" en="Quest categories" /></h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="Adviser 任務" en="Adviser quests" /></strong>: <Bi zh="教學引導，依序完成（蓋第一個建築 / 第一次掠奪 / 升 MB Lv 5 等）。每階段獎勵約 100–500 資源 + 偶爾銀幣或冒險點" en="Tutorial flow, sequential (build first building / first raid / MB Lv 5 etc.). Each rewards ~100–500 resources + occasional silver or adventure points" /></li>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="Daily 任務" en="Daily quests" /></strong>: <Bi zh="每天刷新，做特定動作換獎勵點數" en="Refresh daily, complete specific actions for reward points" /></li>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="World 任務" en="World quests" /></strong>: <Bi zh="長期目標（達 X 人口、佔領 Y 個綠洲），獎勵更大" en="Long-term goals (reach X population, capture Y oases), bigger rewards" /></li>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="Beginner Protection 期間額外獎勵" en="Beginner-protection bonus rewards" /></strong>: <Bi zh="保護期內完成任務有額外資源加成" en="Extra resource bonus on tasks completed during protection" /></li>
  </ul>

  <Callout kind="tip" titleZh="優先做哪些 task" titleEn="Which tasks to prioritize">
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="優先：(1) 一次性的「建造 X / 訓練 Y」任務，不做白不做；(2) 把 spawn 城所有 adviser 任務全跑完，獎勵總和約 5–10k 資源 + 幾百銀幣；(3) Daily quest 集滿換『金幣寶箱』長期值。Skip：太繞路或要花真金的「達 X 人口」之類晚期任務。"
        en="Prioritize: (1) one-shot 'build X / train Y' tasks — free completions; (2) finish ALL adviser tasks on spawn (~5–10k total resources + a few hundred silver); (3) daily quests for the gold-chest long-term grind. Skip: late-game pop-target quests that distract from real planning."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>

  <Callout kind="info" titleZh="任務獎勵會隨英雄等級放大" titleEn="Task rewards scale with hero level">
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="每個任務獎勵的資源量 = 基準值 × (1 + 英雄等級 × 0.02)。也就是每級 +2%。"
        en="Each task reward = base × (1 + hero_level × 0.02). That's +2% per level."
      />
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <Bi
          zh="Lv 0（新手）→ ×1.00（基準值）"
          en="Lv 0 (fresh) → ×1.00 (base)"
        />
      </li>
      <li>
        <Bi
          zh="Lv 25 → ×1.50"
          en="Lv 25 → ×1.50"
        />
      </li>
      <li>
        <Bi
          zh="Lv 50 → ×2.00（雙倍獎勵）"
          en="Lv 50 → ×2.00 (double)"
        />
      </li>
      <li>
        <Bi
          zh="Lv 100 → ×3.00（三倍獎勵）"
          en="Lv 100 → ×3.00 (triple)"
        />
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="策略意義：越晚領任務（拉高英雄等級後）獎勵越大。但別為了多拿 2-5% 而卡住進度 — 卡在 Lv 20 領 vs Lv 22 領只差 4%，不值得延誤。真正值得拖的是重大任務（人口/CP 高 tier）等 Lv 25+ 再領。"
        en="Implication: delaying reward claims until later (higher hero level) means bigger rewards. But don't stall progression for 2-5% — Lv 20 vs Lv 22 is only 4% difference. Only the big-ticket tasks (high-tier Population / CP) are worth holding until Lv 25+."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>

  <details class="task-reward-table">
    <summary>
      <Bi zh="任務獎勵完整對照表（點開展開）" en="Full task reward reference (click to expand)" />
    </summary>

    <p class="table-caption">
      <Bi
        zh="以下全部是 Lv 0 英雄的基準值。你實際拿到 = 基準 × (1 + 英雄 Lv × 0.02)。"
        en="All values below are base rewards (hero Lv 0). Your actual reward = base × (1 + heroLevel × 0.02)."
      />
    </p>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B1. 文化點產量任務（tier 1-7）" en="B1. Culture point production (tier 1-7)" />
    </h4>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th><Bi zh="CP 目標" en="CP target" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="資源" en="Res" /></th>
          <th>Exp</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>1</td><td>50</td><td>1,500</td><td>25</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2</td><td>100</td><td>3,000</td><td>50</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3</td><td>150</td><td>4,500</td><td>75</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4</td><td>250</td><td>6,000</td><td>100</td></tr>
        <tr><td>5</td><td>350</td><td>7,500</td><td>125</td></tr>
        <tr><td>6</td><td>500</td><td>9,000</td><td>150</td></tr>
        <tr><td>7</td><td>750</td><td>10,500</td><td>175</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B2. 人口任務（tier 1-7）" en="B2. Population (tier 1-7)" />
    </h4>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th><Bi zh="人口目標" en="Pop target" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="資源" en="Res" /></th>
          <th>Exp</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>1</td><td>50</td><td>1,500</td><td>25</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2</td><td>100</td><td>3,000</td><td>50</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3</td><td>150</td><td>4,500</td><td>75</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4</td><td>250</td><td>6,000</td><td>100</td></tr>
        <tr><td>5</td><td>350</td><td>7,500</td><td>125</td></tr>
        <tr><td>6</td><td>500</td><td>9,000</td><td>150</td></tr>
        <tr><td>7</td><td>750</td><td>10,500</td><td>175</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B3. 單格資源田升級（Crop / Wood / Clay / Iron，每種資源相同）" en="B3. Field upgrade per resource (Crop / Wood / Clay / Iron — same per resource)" />
    </h4>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th><Bi zh="田等級" en="Field level" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="資源" en="Res" /></th>
          <th>Exp</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>1</td><td>Lv 2</td><td>600</td><td>10</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2</td><td>Lv 4</td><td>1,200</td><td>20</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3</td><td>Lv 7</td><td>1,800</td><td>30</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4</td><td>Lv 10</td><td>2,400</td><td>40</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh={`B4. "全部同種" 資源田（同種 4 格全升到該等級，每種資源相同）`} en={`B4. "All X" fields (all 4 of a type to level — same per resource)`} />
    </h4>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th><Bi zh="等級" en="Level" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="資源" en="Res" /></th>
          <th>Exp</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>1</td><td>Lv 2</td><td>900</td><td>15</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2</td><td>Lv 3</td><td>1,800</td><td>30</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3</td><td>Lv 5</td><td>2,700</td><td>45</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4</td><td>Lv 8</td><td>3,600</td><td>60</td></tr>
        <tr><td>5</td><td>Lv 10</td><td>4,500</td><td>75</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B5a. 均衡升田（每種田各一格升到 Lv X）" en="B5a. Even growth (1 of each field type to Lv X)" />
    </h4>
    <p class="table-caption">
      <Bi
        zh={`xlsx 原始標籤為「1 van elk X」（荷蘭文：每種 X 一個）。每種田（Crop / Wood / Clay / Iron）各取一格，全部升到指定等級時觸發。`}
        en={`xlsx label: "1 van elk X" (Dutch for "one of each X"). Triggered when one field of each type (Crop / Wood / Clay / Iron) reaches the target level.`}
      />
    </p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th><Bi zh="等級" en="Level" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="資源" en="Res" /></th>
          <th>Exp</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>1</td><td>Lv 2</td><td>300</td><td>5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2</td><td>Lv 4</td><td>600</td><td>10</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3</td><td>Lv 7</td><td>900</td><td>15</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4</td><td>Lv 10</td><td>1,200</td><td>20</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B5b. 全資源田同升級（每種田的每一格都升到 Lv X）" en="B5b. All fields to level (every field of every type to Lv X)" />
    </h4>
    <p class="table-caption">
      <Bi
        zh="村內全部 18 格資源田（4 Crop + 4 Wood + 4 Clay + 4 Iron + 2 額外 Crop）都升到指定等級時觸發，獎勵為 B5a 的 8 倍。"
        en="Triggered when all 18 fields in the village (4 Crop + 4 Wood + 4 Clay + 4 Iron + 2 extra Crop) reach the target level. Rewards are 8× B5a."
      />
    </p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th><Bi zh="等級" en="Level" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="資源" en="Res" /></th>
          <th>Exp</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>1</td><td>All Lv 2</td><td>2,400</td><td>40</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2</td><td>All Lv 4</td><td>4,800</td><td>80</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3</td><td>All Lv 7</td><td>7,200</td><td>120</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4</td><td>All Lv 8</td><td>9,600</td><td>160</td></tr>
        <tr><td>5</td><td>All Lv 9</td><td>12,000</td><td>200</td></tr>
        <tr><td>6</td><td>All Lv 10</td><td>14,400</td><td>240</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B6. 軍事與經濟建設（Warehouse / Granary / Barracks / Stable）" en="B6. Military & economy buildings (Warehouse / Granary / Barracks / Stable)" />
    </h4>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th><Bi zh="建築" en="Building" /></th>
          <th>Lv 1</th>
          <th>Lv 3</th>
          <th>Lv 7</th>
          <th>Lv 12</th>
          <th>Lv 20</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Warehouse</td><td>300</td><td>600</td><td>900</td><td>1,200</td><td>1,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Granary</td><td>300</td><td>600</td><td>900</td><td>1,200</td><td>1,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Barracks</td><td>300</td><td>600</td><td>900</td><td>1,200</td><td>1,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Stable</td><td>600</td><td>1,200</td><td>1,800</td><td>2,400</td><td>3,000</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B6b. 其他基礎建設（村政 / 防禦 / 外交）" en="B6b. Other infrastructure (admin / defense / diplomacy)" />
    </h4>
    <p class="table-caption">
      <Bi
        zh="不同建築採用不同等級分段。Workshop / Embassy 只在 Lv 1 給一次獎勵。Rally Point 只在 Lv 1 / 10 / 20。Cranny 止於 Lv 10。每一 tier 的 Exp = Res ÷ 60。"
        en="Different buildings use different level breakpoints. Workshop / Embassy reward once at Lv 1 only. Rally Point has only Lv 1 / 10 / 20. Cranny stops at Lv 10. Per tier, Exp = Res ÷ 60."
      />
    </p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th><Bi zh="建築" en="Building" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="等級分段" en="Level breakpoints" /></th>
          <th><Bi zh="各 tier 資源（Lv 最低 → 最高）" en="Res per tier (lowest → highest Lv)" /></th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Main Building</td><td>Lv 1 / 3 / 7 / 12 / 20</td><td>600 / 1,200 / 1,800 / 2,400 / 3,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Marketplace</td><td>Lv 1 / 3 / 7 / 12 / 20</td><td>600 / 1,200 / 1,800 / 2,400 / 3,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Wall</td><td>Lv 1 / 3 / 7 / 12 / 20</td><td>600 / 1,200 / 1,800 / 2,400 / 3,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Residence / Palace</td><td>Lv 1 / 3 / 7 / 10 / 20</td><td>1,200 / 2,400 / 3,600 / 4,800 / 6,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Cranny</td><td>Lv 1 / 3 / 6 / 10</td><td>300 / 600 / 900 / 1,200</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rally Point</td><td>Lv 1 / 10 / 20</td><td>600 / 1,200 / 1,800</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Workshop</td><td>Lv 1</td><td>2,400</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Embassy</td><td>Lv 1</td><td>1,200</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>
      <Bi zh="B7. Academy / Smithy / Town Hall（僅 Lv 1 / 10 / 20）" en="B7. Academy / Smithy / Town Hall (only Lv 1 / 10 / 20)" />
    </h4>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th><Bi zh="建築" en="Building" /></th>
          <th>Lv 1</th>
          <th>Lv 10</th>
          <th>Lv 20</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Academy</td><td>600</td><td>1,200</td><td>1,800</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Smithy</td><td>600</td><td>1,200</td><td>1,800</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Town Hall</td><td>2,400</td><td>4,800</td><td>7,200</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </details>

  <p style="font-size: var(--fs-sm); color: var(--text-2);">
    <Bi
      zh="任務獎勵可以等到當下需要時才領（按下 Adviser → Reward 領取）。Lumi 建議：要訓開拓者前一刻才領，因為剛好把成本補回來。"
      en="Rewards can be claimed on demand (Adviser → Reward). Lumi tip: hold off claiming until just before training Settlers — the rewards conveniently offset Settler cost."
    />
  </p>
</Section>

<style>
  .task-reward-table {
    margin: 16px 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-0);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--bg-1);
    padding: 12px 16px;
  }
  .task-reward-table summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 0;
  }
  .task-reward-table .table-caption {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 8px 0 12px;
  }
  .task-reward-table h4 {
    margin: 16px 0 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-0);
  }
  .task-reward-table table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .task-reward-table th,
  .task-reward-table td {
    padding: 4px 8px;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-0);
  }
  .task-reward-table td {
    font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
    color: var(--text-1);
  }
  .task-reward-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
</style>
